10 minutes tops. Pull off old, glue in new. Notice orientation of old one 
and compare that to new one.

Busdepot, West Coast Metric, and others sell good replacements.

Use 3M weatherstrip glue. Avalibable at most FLAPS.

Normally very bright yellow.


